-- XL Gets Regulatory Approval to Establish Operations in Brazil
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2012-01-05T13:14:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-05/xl-gets-regulatory-approval-to-establish-operations-in-brazil.html
XL Group Plc (XL) , the seller of insurance
and reinsurance, received approval from regulators to establish
operations in  Brazil .  “Brazil is at the intersection of global development,
connectivity and growth,” XL Chief Executive Officer Mike McGavick said in a statement today distributed by PR Newswire.
“We are thrilled to expand our operations in the country.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in  New York  at 
